H_n(x)=(-1)^ne^{x^2}\dfrac{d^n}{dx^n}e^{-x^2}=\dfrac{(-1)^ne^{x^2}}{\sqrt\pi}\dfrac{d^n}{dx^n}\int_0^\infty e^{-\frac{t^2}{4}}\cos xt~dt=\dfrac{(-1)^ne^{x^2}}{\sqrt\pi}\int_0^\infty t^ne^{-\frac{t^2}{4}}\cos\left(xt+\dfrac{n\pi}{2}\right)dt
